An example of long-format fusion/sv files

Source: R/data.R
sv_long.Rd

This set was created from a sample of 30 patients from publicly available non-small cell lung cancer data from GENIEBPC (cohort = 'NSCLC', version = 'v2.0-public')

Usage

sv_long

Format

A data frame with 30 unique sample_id values and 62 hugo symbols listed

Source

https://www.aacr.org/professionals/research/aacr-project-genie/bpc/
